Description: A unified framework for clustering, consensus meta-clustering,
    validation, exploratory interpretation, prediction, and standardized
    plotting. The package provides a native clustering grammar centered on
    cluster(), metacluster(), validate(), explore(), predict(), and plot
    helpers.
